headline: FactSet Kepler Cheuvreux Deal Puts EMEA Research And Valuation In Focus
summary: FactSet Research Systems (NYSE:FDS) has entered a partnership with Kepler Cheuvreux to integrate premium Aftermarket Research into its platform for EMEA clients. The collaboration brings Kepler Cheuvreux's proprietary research and analyst network into FactSet's workflow tools, supported by AI features designed to improve discoverability and usability. The enhanced research access is aimed at institutional clients across Europe, the Middle East, and Africa, with a focus on deeper coverage of...
